Using recycled materials is one of the ways we can lower the carbon impact of our products, since these materials often have a lower carbon footprint than materials from primary sources.

The copper core part is reinforced with UV glue to prevent the solder joints from falling off. The USB C port pass Load-bearing 13KG test which longer service life and will never break.
